text:
(1) A general view east from 58th St., at about 54th Drive, a section of Maspeth Brook, from 58th St. to Broad Street (now 59th Street), showing in the view a part of the Adlers Monument Works.

March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, looking southwest, showing a house on the west side of 58th Street, at about 55th Ave.

February 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: General view - Queens - 58th Street - 54th Drive (East).
